-clashes-with-settlers-and-soldiers-in-west-bank/0000018e-fe95-de5a-a9ef-fffd67950000</link><description>以色列人在约旦河西岸被埋设的爆炸装置炸伤 ■ 巴勒斯坦妇女在世界银行检查站试图刺伤士兵时被杀 ■ 以色列国防军：不了解美国制裁 Netzah Yehuda 营的决定 ■ 哈马斯首领哈尼亚的妹妹被指控煽动，同情恐怖组织 ■ MK Tibi 请求高等法院允许 MK 探视巴勒斯坦安全囚犯</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 03:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article-live/palestinian-killed-in-clashes-with-settlers-and-soldiers-in-west-bank/0000018e-fe95-de5a-a9ef-fffd67950000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列反应有限，但与伊朗的现状已被打破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-limited-response-the-status-quo-with-iran-has-been-breached/0000018e-fd2b-db42-a99f-fdbf3b1d0000</link><description>以色列和伊朗之间的最新一轮袭击凸显了内塔尼亚胡在这一问题上缺乏全面的战略。虽然以色列对结果感到满意，但美国和海湾国家担心地区局势升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 03:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-limited-response-the-status-quo-with-iran-has-been-breached/0000018e-fd2b-db42-a99f-fdbf3b1d0000</guid></item><item><title>上次协议签署五个月后，内塔尼亚胡的举动仍未释放剩余人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/five-months-after-last-deal-netanyahus-moves-have-not-freed-the-remaining-hostages/0000018e-fd2b-d6a0-a9ef-fdbf6e090000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡声称通过军事压力释放人质的口号未能兑现其承诺。他对政府中极端主义分子的政治依赖也无济于事</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 21:35:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/five-months-after-last-deal-netanyahus-moves-have-not-freed-the-remaining-hostages/0000018e-fd2b-d6a0-a9ef-fdbf6e090000</guid></item><item><title>“这个政府必须明白，它没有统治的合法性”：数千名以色列人抗议新选举、人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/this-govt-must-understand-it-has-no-legitimacy-to-rule/0000018e-fce0-db42-a99f-fdfff1d00000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、贝尔谢巴、凯撒利亚和海法的多个地点都发生了抗议活动</description><pu